---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — The Lead Letter" description="About The Lead Letter, EntrLabs, and Joseph E. Iesue.">
  <article class="about-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <p class="kicker">The Publication</p>
      <h1>About The Lead Letter</h1>
      <div class="rule-double slim" aria-hidden="true"></div>
    </header>

    <div class="about-body">
      <p class="lede">
        The Lead Letter is a weekly publication on leadership, service, and the discipline of helping
        people rise. It is written for people who lead — formally or not — and who take that
        responsibility seriously.
      </p>
      <p>
        The Lead Letter is published by
        <a href="https://entr.cc/entrlabs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">EntrLabs</a>,
        a research lab of <a href="https://entr.cc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ENTR</a>. EntrLabs
        translates leadership research, learning science, and organizational theory into practical
        systems; The Lead Letter is where that work reaches a public audience, one idea at a time.
      </p>
      <p>
        It is written by <a href="https://josephiesue.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Joseph E. Iesue</a>,
        a leadership researcher and practitioner. His frameworks — Service Leadership, String Leadership,
        and ELEM — inform the thinking behind each letter.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="end-mark"><span>— Strength Through Service —</span></p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
